Description: Hello ! Up for sale is a terrific hollow body electric guitar by Ibanez....the Artcore AGR73T ! This thing is beautiful ! And yes, I am talking about its looks! And the sustain that this thing produces....it's so sweet ! Want to add some flare and character to your notes? Take a bend on the Bigsby-type Ibanez Tremolo....it stays in tune well and does exactly what a whammy bar of its kind is supposed to do ! And this girl plays so well and easy! You want to shred some jazz fusion or some neo-classical metal? You can do it with the Artcore ! You don't have to play just jazz, Christian music, or rockabilly with this thing! Plus, additional "safety features," such as some really cool and sturdy strap locks that the previous owner installed, as well as a padded gig bag that will provide an extra layer of protection from the rigors of shipping in addition to our careful packing, which are also included with this listing, really add value to this already amazingly priced guitar...I feel like we're selling an expensive luxury car ! Such versatility, functionality and sonic coupled with a striking, eye catching appearance makes this a guitar that you will not want to pass up....get it now before someone with same idea beats you to it ! Please read the condition description, these listing details, and examine the pictures carefully. Thanks so much for your interest and I hope you buy it now!!!
